text: Carrie Smith (born 28 January 1995) is an Australian competitive sailor. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, in the women's 470 class. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Australian female sailors (sport) Category:Olympic sailors of Australia Category:Sailors at the 2016 Summer Olympics – 470
